{"id":495815610,"lang":"cpp","time":"2 weeks, 5 days","timestamp":1621521177,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"24 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/495815610/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Ugly Number II","memory":"7.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    typedef long long int ll;\n    int nthUglyNumber(int n) {\n        priority_queue<ll,vector<ll>,greater<>> minq;\n        minq.push(1);\n        if(n==1) return 1;\n        ll cnt =1;\n        while(cnt<n){\n            ll temp = minq.top();\n            minq.pop();\n            if(temp%2==0){\n                minq.push(temp*2);\n            } else if(temp%3==0){\n                minq.push(temp*2);\n                minq.push(temp*3);\n            } else{\n                minq.push(temp*2);\n                minq.push(temp*3);\n                minq.push(temp*5);\n            }\n            cnt++;\n        }\n        return minq.top();\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"ugly-number-ii"}
